query: ATTACH MATERIALIZED VIEW default.fact_agg_5min_mv UUID 'ecc5563e-7bb9-47a4-b3cc-5bf403d72181' TO default.fact_agg_5min_local (`subscriber_key` String, `start_time_5min` DateTime, `end_time_5min` DateTime, `int_ipv4` IPv4, `app_key` LowCardinality(String), `uli` String, `volume_in` UInt64, `volume_out` UInt64) AS SELECT subscriber_key, toStartOfFiveMinute(start_time) AS start_time_5min, toStartOfFiveMinute(end_time) AS end_time_5min, int_ipv4, app_key, uli, sum(volume_in) AS volume_in, sum(volume_out) AS volume_out FROM default.fact_rt_local GROUP BY subscriber_key, start_time_5min, end_time_5min, int_ipv4, app_key, uli
